**********************************************************************************
********************************** Awesome Features ******************************
**********************************************************************************

1. It shows a list of links from the database
2. New links can be added
3. Links can be tagged
4. Links can be filtered by a tag
5. Sort by time added


                                   SO AWESOME!!!

***********************************************************************************
************************************ User Stories *********************************
***********************************************************************************

(1)

As a user,
So that i can go to websites that visit frequently,
I'd like to display a list links to websites.

(2)

As a user,
So that I can update the list of bookmarks,
I'd like to add links and title to a website that I like.

(3)

As a user,
So that I can keep organize my links,
I want to be able to tag them.

(4)

As a user,
So that I can search for websites based on a topic,
I want to filter links by tag.

(5)

As a user,
So I can see my latest bookmarks,
I want to be able to sort by time added.

***********************************************************************************
************************************ Classes **************************************
***********************************************************************************

- User: tracks identity
- Bookmark manager: manages bookmarks (add, sort, filter)
- Bookmark: tracks the website URL, blurb and tag info
- Tags: categories


                                  Kind of like
